{"tid":1702627,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Twitter戰線]監警會國際專家小組成員在個人Twitter帳戶代小組發聲明 建議由獨立機構調查近期事件","createTime":"2019-11-09T19:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T07:01:47.000Z","uid":273116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3268128c300dda6aae0f5cd12e55008c3176b3eb","tid":1702627,"uid":273116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T19:36:29.000Z","msg":"監警會國際專家小組聲明　建議由獨立機構調查近期事件 2019-11-10 RTHK 02:11<br />\n<br />\n監警會國際專家小組成員Clifford Stott在個人Twitter帳戶代小組發聲明，表示經過分析，認為監警會的權力及獨立調查能力不足應付近期事件的規模，亦不符合重視自由與權利社會的國際監警察組織標準。小組建議下一步由獨立機構深入調查。<br />\n<br />\n聲明認為，監警會需要大幅擴大能力，包括可向警方及其他機構取得清晰的事實；及時接觸重要的文件；以及向重要的證人取證等。<br />\n<br />\n國際專家小組認為，監警會仍可以作出中期報告，提供有限的事實，但只足以作初步結論，而前提是監警會要短期內審視資源及程序。小組認為，下一步若能由具必要權力的獨立機構，進行深入及全面的調查，將更令人信服。<br />\n<br />\n監警會就6月以來的反修例示威成立專責委員會，預計年底交報告，其後邀請5名國際專家供意見，其中Clifford Stott為英國基爾大學自然科學研究院院長。<br />\n<br />\n新聞link：<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491048-20191110.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491048-20191110.htm&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpujOHetkdf0TruP2VOJ8R9E%3D&h=12f25cf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491048-20191110.htm&h=20461da5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491048-20191110.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter link: <a href=\"http://twitter.com/cliffordstott/status/1193086839416078336?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcliffordstott%2Fstatus%2F1193086839416078336%3Fs%3D21&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpujOHetkdf0TruP2VOJ8R9E%3D&h=01919ff7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcliffordstott%2Fstatus%2F1193086839416078336%3Fs%3D21&h=9f43521a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/cliffordstott/status/1193086839416078336?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ohx0X7n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhx0X7n.png&h=442093ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyqaAT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyqaAT4.jpg&h=90765369&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OhOrTFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhOrTFL.jpg&h=919fb642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有twitter嘅幫手retweet、like同comments。"},{"pid":"624ea6c8de036244ee1a8e8b794aaeefd4373723","tid":1702627,"uid":4635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T19:52:19.000Z","msg":"777聽日就炒晒班專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a26d2777eb9cc25204b9d643a7d9429cbf9dfb","tid":1702627,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T19:58:44.000Z","msg":"777請佢地果陣有冇諗過有前科既人都忍唔撚到班強姦殺人犯"},{"pid":"2cc5aef277e2cfc763c2b8653466c131b49fbbdc","tid":1702627,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9a26d2777eb9cc25204b9d643a7d9429cbf9dfb","tid":1702627,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T19:58:44.000Z","msg":"777請佢地果陣有冇諗過有前科既人都忍唔撚到班強姦殺人犯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T20:06:19.000Z","msg":"果班專家的幫手蓋過的臭史其實只係小學級別<br />\n絕對無輪姦,殺人扮自殺"},{"pid":"47a21452913ce1b7f4433ec1888acc18f8f669f9","tid":1702627,"uid":7849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T20:06:39.000Z","msg":"外國勢力妄圖對中国內政香港警務指手劃腳，<br />\n特區政府予於嚴厲譴責。"},{"pid":"390ebca42a61eb5391fa63a3d3627ccaadc3c6dd","tid":1702627,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T20:07:31.000Z","msg":"出報告但唔公開<br />\n<br />\n公開但唔理"},{"pid":"cde4c3e1f0f3ac071f33179c405aaacd1dbe239e","tid":1702627,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T20:08:15.000Z","msg":"專家心諗想拉埋我落水<br />\n<br />\n拿拿聲割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a7f38d18982d6fcf7984561462996ebc1a5a53","t